targets.queryText: SELECT CAST(strftime(timestamp_capture_packet) as INTEGER) as time, count(*) as Normal from Packet_Informations INNER JOIN Image_Classification on Packet_Informations.packet_informations_id = Image_Classification.packet_informations_id INNER JOIN Packet_Data on Packet_Data.packet_data_id = Packet_informations.packet_data_id where classification = 'Normal' group by time order by time
